#<AdxTL>@(#)8.0.0.0 $Revision$
GBIDC1="" : GBIDC2=""
Raz GPILOBJ, GPILCOD
Call OBJET("AOE",GBIDC2,GBIDC3) From GOBJET
End

$ACTION
Case ACTION
 When "INIT_DIA" : Gosub INIT_DIA
 When "EXEC"     : Gosub EXEC
Endcase
Return

$INIT_DIA
Raz [M:AOE9]
J = 0
For I=0 To [M:AOE2]NBRLIG-1
 If find([M:AOE2]SEL(I),2,3)
  Read [ATB]CODFIC = [M:AOE2]FIL(I)
  K = instr(1,[M:AOE2]FLD(I),"(")
  If K
   ZONE1 = left$([M:AOE2]FLD(I),K-1)
  Else
   ZONE1 = [M:AOE2]FLD(I)
  Endif
  Read [ATZ]CODZONE  = [F:ATB]CODFIC;ZONE1
  Read [ATY]CODTYP   = [F:ATZ]CODTYP
  [M:AOE9]TABCONT(J) = "[F:"+[F:ATB]ABRFIC+"]"+ZONE1
  [M:AOE9]NUM(J)     = I
  [M:AOE9]CODTYP(J)  = [F:ATY]CODTYP
  [M:AOE9]TYP(J)     = [F:ATY]TYPTYP
  Call TEXTE([F:ATZ]NOCOURT,[M:AOE9]BNOM(J)) From OBJDIV
  [M:AOE9]BDEB(J) = [M:AOE2]STRVAL(I)
  [M:AOE9]BFIN(J) = [M:AOE2]ENDVAL(I)
  Case [F:ATY]CODTYP
   When "AXX","AX1","AX2","AX3"
    If [F:ATY]LNGTYP<>0
     [M:AOE9]LONG(J)  = [F:ATY]LNGTYP
    Elsif [F:ATZ]LONG<>0
     [M:AOE9]LONG(J)  = [F:ATZ]LONG
    Else
     [M:AOE9]LONG(J)   = GLONDES
    Endif
   When "ADI"
    Read [AMP]CODPAR=2;[F:ATB]CODFIC;[F:ATZ]CODZONE;"ADI"
    If !fstat
     [M:AOE9]NOLIB(J) = val(num$(evalue([F:AMP]VALPAR)))
    Endif
    [M:AOE9]LONG(J)  = GLONADI
   When Default
    Case [F:ATY]TYPTYP
     When 1
      If [F:ATY]NOLIB<>0
       [M:AOE9]NOLIB(J) = [F:ATY]NOLIB
      Else
       [M:AOE9]NOLIB(J) = [F:ATZ]NOLIB
      Endif
     When 8
     When Default
      If [M:AOE9]TYP(J)=7
       If [F:ATY]LNGTYP<>0
        [M:AOE9]LONG(J)  = [F:ATY]LNGTYP
       Else
        [M:AOE9]LONG(J)  = [F:ATZ]LONG
       Endif
      Endif
    Endcase
  Endcase
  Call CHARGE([M:AOE9]BDEB(J),[M:AOE9]CODTYP(J),[M:AOE9]NOLIB(J)
&              ,[M:AOE9]LONG(J),[M:AOE9]STRVAL(J)) From FMTVAR
  Call CHARGE([M:AOE9]BFIN(J),[M:AOE9]CODTYP(J),[M:AOE9]NOLIB(J)
&              ,[M:AOE9]LONG(J),[M:AOE9]ENDVAL(J)) From FMTVAR
  J += 1
 Endif
Next I
[M:AOE9]NBCLE = J
[M:AOE9]NBFIC = 0
For I=0 To [M:AOE2]NBRLIG-1
 If !find([M:AOE2]FIL(I),[M:AOE9]FICHIER(0..[M:AOE9]NBFIC-1))
  [M:AOE9]FICHIER([M:AOE9]NBFIC) = [M:AOE2]FIL(I)
  K = find([M:AOE9]FICHIER([M:AOE9]NBFIC),[M:AOE1]FIL)
  If K
   [M:AOE9]FLGEXP([M:AOE9]NBFIC)  = [M:AOE1]FLGEXP(K-1)
  Endif
  [M:AOE9]NBFIC += 1
 Endif
Next I
Return

$EXEC
# X3-57656 04.10.2018
Raz [M:AOE1]UPDFLG
For I=0 To [M:AOE9]NBCLE-1
 If [M:AOE2]STRVAL([M:AOE9]NUM(I)) <> [M:AOE9]STRVAL(I) or [M:AOE2]ENDVAL([M:AOE9]NUM(I)) <> [M:AOE9]ENDVAL(I)
  [M:AOE1]UPDFLG = [V]CST_AYES
 Endif
 [M:AOE2]STRVAL([M:AOE9]NUM(I)) = [M:AOE9]STRVAL(I)
 [M:AOE2]ENDVAL([M:AOE9]NUM(I)) = [M:AOE9]ENDVAL(I)
Next I
For I=0 To [M:AOE9]NBFIC-1
 If [M:AOE1]FIL(I) <> [M:AOE9]FICHIER(I) or [M:AOE1]FLGEXP(I) <> [M:AOE9]FLGEXP(I)
  [M:AOE1]UPDFLG = [V]CST_AYES
 Endif
 [M:AOE1]FIL(I)    = [M:AOE9]FICHIER(I)
 [M:AOE1]FLGEXP(I) = [M:AOE9]FLGEXP(I)
Next I
Return

######################################################################################
Subprog AS_NBCLE
If !([M]NBCLE<>0) : mkstat = 2 : Endif
End

Subprog AS_BDEB(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Gosub P1_AS_B
If mkstat : Raz [M]STRVAL(nolign-1) : Endif
End

Subprog AM_BDEB(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INF
Case [M]TYP(nolign-1)
 When 1,2,3,4,5,6
  If val([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<>0 & val([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<val([M]STRVAL(nolign-1)) : INF = 1 : Endif
 When 7
  If [M]ENDVAL(nolign-1)<>"" & [M]ENDVAL(nolign-1)<[M]STRVAL(nolign-1) : INF = 1 : Endif
 When 8
  If gdat$([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<>[0/0/0] & gdat$([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<gdat$([M]STRVAL(nolign-1))
   INF = 1
  Endif
Endcase
If INF
 [M]BFIN(nolign-1) = VALEUR
 Call CONTROLE([M]BFIN(nolign-1),[M]CODTYP(nolign-1),[M]NOLIB(nolign-1)
&              ,[M]LONG(nolign-1),[M]ENDVAL(nolign-1)) From FMTVAR
 Affzo [M]BFIN(nolign-1)
Endif
End

Subprog AS_BFIN(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Gosub P1_AS_B
If mkstat : Raz [M]ENDVAL(nolign-1) : Endif
End

$P1_AS_B
# dans GX, pour un modèle associé à un objet géré par déposant, si le site et le déposant
# de la table associée au modèle sont des critères du modèle et si site début<>site fin
# ou site début=vide, on ne saisit pas les bornes déposants
If GPRODUIT=1 & [M:AOE1]OBJ<>"" & [M:AOE2]FIL([M]NUM(nolign-1))=[M:AOE1]FLGFIL(0)
 Gosub SETCLE From ="WO"+[M:AOE1]OBJ
 If nolign>1 & dim([L]CLEDEP)>0 & [L]CLEDEP<>"" & [M:AOE2]FLD([M]NUM(nolign-1))=[L]CLEDEP
& & [M:AOE2]FIL([M]NUM(nolign-2))=[M:AOE2]FIL([M]NUM(nolign-1))
& & [M:AOE2]FLD([M]NUM(nolign-2))=[L]CLEFCY
& & ([M]BDEB(nolign-2)<>[M]BFIN(nolign-2) | [M]BDEB(nolign-2)="")
   mkstat=1 : Return
 Endif
Endif
Return

Subprog C_BFIN(VALPAR)
Variable Char VALPAR()
Local Integer OK
OK = 1
Case [M]TYP(nolign-1)
 When 1,2,3,4,5,6
  If val([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<>0 & val([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<val([M]STRVAL(nolign-1)) : OK = 0 : Endif
 When 7
  If [M]ENDVAL(nolign-1)<>"" & [M]ENDVAL(nolign-1)<[M]STRVAL(nolign-1) : OK = 0 : Endif
 When 8
  If gdat$([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<>[0/0/0] & gdat$([M]ENDVAL(nolign-1))<gdat$([M]STRVAL(nolign-1))
   OK = 0
  Endif
Endcase
If !OK
 GMESSAGE = mess(8,135,1) : # Valeur trop petite
 mkstat = 2 : End
Endif
Gosub P1_C_BFIN
End

$P1_C_BFIN
If GPRODUIT=1 & [M:AOE1]OBJ<>"" & [M:AOE2]FIL([M]NUM(nolign-1))=[M:AOE1]FLGFIL(0)
 Gosub SETCLE From ="WO"+[M:AOE1]OBJ
 If dim([L]CLEFCY)>0 & [L]CLEFCY<>"" & [M:AOE2]FLD([M]NUM(nolign-1))=[L]CLEFCY
  If [M]BDEB(nolign-1)=VALPAR & VALPAR<>""
   [M]FCY=VALPAR
  Else
   [M]FCY=""
  Endif
 Elsif dim([L]CLEDEP)>0 & [L]CLEDEP<>"" & [M:AOE2]FLD([M]NUM(nolign-1))=[L]CLEDEP
  If [M]BDEB(nolign-1)=VALPAR & VALPAR<>""
   [M]DEP=VALPAR
  Else
   [M]DEP=""
  Endif
 Endif
Endif
Return

